    "whyTitle": "Why We Launched Buthaina Platform:",
    "whyIntro": "Driven by our belief in partnership with government and commercial entities, and recognizing the market need, we launched the platform for the following reasons:",
    "whyPoints": [
      "The workload in this sector is increasing with Vision 2030.",
      "Low-current systems are essential in most projects.",
      "Reduce costs and ease the burden on establishments.",
      "Lack of experience among some subcontractors.",
      "Specialization and professionalism are top priorities.",
      "Quick response is required in many services.",
      "Professional standards and commitments ensure quality execution."
